text: Selangor (also known as Selangor Darul Ehsan or Selangor the Abode of Sincerity) is one of the states that form Malaysia. It is located in peninsular Malaysia. The state surrounds Kuala Lumpur and Putrajaya. == References == == Other websites == * Official website * Rail map of Selangor * Geographical maps of Selangor * History of Selangor * Selangor Marketplace
